Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HowllYe&\fs18\fn굴림}오타 및 오역수정은 개인에 한해서 해주십시오.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,우후~우후~ 조인다.조여. 으헤헤헤~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,으헤헤헤~ 한번이라도 좋으니까
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,너희같이 제복입은 년들을 범해보고 싶었다구. 헤헤헤헤~~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:00:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,가..갈것같아
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,슬슬 메인디쉬를 먹어볼까~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,(다들 아시죠? 흑마서에 관련된 자들이 외우는 주문임)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:02:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,싫어... 싫어!! 아앗!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HAqua&\fs18\fn굴림}바이블 블랙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HRed&\fs18\fn굴림}제2장 Reunion ~재회~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,싫..어..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,롱기누스의 창..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,아키군! 어이! 아키군!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:05:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,유게..과장님..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,검안실
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,(주문 좀 멋있게 좀 지어보지..좀..)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,위문갔다 오라더니 시체해부를 같이하라는건 또 뭔지..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,저렇게 불가사의한 시체분을 뵙는건 처음이야.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,남자쪽은 탄화할때까지 타버렸는데
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,여자쪽은 상처하나 없이 깨끗하니..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만 주임.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,확실히 이 일은 우리들 손에서 벗어나 특련의 련중으로..아!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,해부소견만큼은
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,관할인 우리가 써 재출하지 않으면 안되는거야.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,아무래도 그들은 연구기관이란 명목의 민간인 모임이니까.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,아! 그..그렇네요.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,어헉!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,어..어떻게 이런일이!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,왜 그러는데요?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,어헉!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:08:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐라고? 시체가 되살아났다고?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,네? 네.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,지금 막 관할의 케이지씨한테서 전화가..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,이게 그 자료입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,토도 유키.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,회음부 질곡 및 음부에 찰과상이 인정돼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,본인의 소견대로 소실된 담임교사
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,요시타니 교사에게 강간당했을 가능성 있음.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,그밖에 이상은 없고 극히 건강했으며
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,정신적으로도 안정돼있었고
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,데리러 온 가족과 함께 귀가시켰습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘부터 신학기..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,제가 학원상황등을 포함해서 보고 오겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,그래. 가면실에서 조금 쉬다가 갔다 오도록.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇게 하도록 하겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,이마리 주임. 왠지 분위기가 이상해..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,네가 정신을 잃고있던 사이 여러가지 일이 있었던 거겠지.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,그것보다, 아키군! 은행에서 알아낸 자료는?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,아앗! 네. 지금 바로.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,대출담보중에서 그것만 없어졌다고 합니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,은행 습격자들이 모두 죽어버렸다는건..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,자네와 이마리군이 사로잡히기 이전에
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,뭔가 특이사항이 있었는지 생각해보게.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,이마리주임과 전 학원옥상에서 소실되있던
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,요시타니 교사의 아버지인 고고학자
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,요시타니 소우지가 대출담보로 맡겨둔 것을 확인하기위해
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,그 병원에..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:10:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,흐음..렌즈쿠료,키사쯔진 사건과 어떤 관련이 있을까..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,그 요시타니 소우지도 반년전부터 행방불명.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,유적발굴차 나간다고 말한 모양이지만..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,국내/외 할것없이
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,광신적인 악마숭배 컬트수단을 모두 철저하게 밝혀내라.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,아키군! 자네는 발견한 것의 내력과 함께
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,이마리군과 학원을 확실히 조사해라.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,옙!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,사에키 선생님. 무슨일입니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,교토 선생님.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게 이른시간부터 죄송합니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,아닙니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:10:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,언제나 교육에 힘쓰시는 사에키 선생님의 부탁이라면..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,어쨋든 오늘부터 신학기니까요.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,고마워요.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,드세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,아아.. 언제 먹어도 사에키선생이 끓여준 차는 ダ羚楮?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,으음? 여느때보다 조금 쓴맛이..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,네에. 여느때보다 조금 많이..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,네?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,그것보다.. 교토선생님. 부탁드리고 싶은 일이..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,들어오세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,아..네.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:12:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,이 학교에 이런 지하도가 있었다니..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,여기가 수도원이었을때의 흔적이죠.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,저희들이 학생이었을때
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,키타미 레이카 선생님께서 알려주셨어요.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,아아~ 사에키선생은 여기 졸업생이었군요.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,그러고보니
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘부터 대리교사로 오는 시라키선생도
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,이곳 졸업생이라고 했던가..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,그녀. 저와 동기생이에요.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,그건 그렇고 방학중에 학원에서 사건이 있었던듯 해요.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,사..사에키 선생님. 어디서 그런 정보를..?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,사건에 우연히 말려들게된 학생회장 키리야 사키상에게서..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,키리야군으로부터 어떤 얘기를 들으셨는지 모르겠지만
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,경찰의 조사에 의하면 그녀를 연모하던
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,담임 요시타니 선생이
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,마음을 잘못먹고 그녀를 강간하고나서
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,자신의 잘못이 큰걸 깨닫고 분신자살했다고..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,어머.. 무서워요.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,사건쪽은 학원장과 그녀의 아버지인 토도 리지쪼가
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,경찰을 설득해 은폐를..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,그저 걱정되는건 토도군이 받은 정신적충격의 후유증쪽이..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,상냥하시네요. 교토선생님.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,으앗!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,이..이건..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,토도..군..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,으..으아..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:14:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,쿄토선생님.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘은 쿄토선생님께
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,생도관 임원들이 꼭 부탁드리고 싶은 일이 있다고..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,부탁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,우웁!! 토..토도군!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,너..너희들.. 대체 무슨..?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,(부럽다.. 6 : 1 플레이라니..)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:16:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,금속성분?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,예. 철,탄소,니켈,크롬,몰리브텐.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,거기에 미약하지만 망간,텅스텐,바나디움,티탄,코볼트..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,그거 그 조각의 성분원소지?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,은행의 대출담보로 남겨져있던 이것이..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,대출담보목록에 남겨져 있던 흔적으로 조사해봤는데
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,그에따르면 창의 끝부분으로 쓰였고 이가 대부분 빠져있었다고..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,그것도 5천년전에 합금주조 됐고 창과 함께일 가능성이..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,롱기누스의 창..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,네에?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐예요 그게?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,10시간에 걸쳐서 예수의 옆구리를 꿰뚫어 버린 창.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:17:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,지하실?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,이곳에 뭔가가?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,아아아..사에키 선생님..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,전부터..하아아.. 선생님을..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,아아~ 교토선생님. 마음껏 해도 좋아요.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,자극이 너무 강했으려나? 처녀인 당신에게는.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,아앙. 거기가 아니에요.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,아아아.. 넣고 싶어.. 아아..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,넣어줘요. 교토선생님.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:20:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,더..더 세게 해주세요. 아아~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:21:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,저건 대체 무슨 의식이지?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.96,0:21:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,검은 세상을 부활시키기 위한 전희...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,의식은 이제부터야.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,그건?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:21:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,핫!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,의식이.. 시작된다..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,서둘러야돼.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,하악!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.74,0:22:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,조디..클로리..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:23:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,이..마리..주임..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,이건..내게..무엇을..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,수고했어요. 사에키상. 꽤나 기다리도록 만들어버렸네.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,아니요. 다시 만나게되서 기뻐요. 키타미 선생님.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,키..키타미 선생님? 이마리 주임이?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,아?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:26:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.03,0:26:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,계속...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.62,0:26:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.45,0:26:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,드디어 끝났군요.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.41,0:26:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.41,0:26:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,제 두번째 번역작임과 동시에 자막은 처음 만들어 보는거라
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.12,0:26:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.12,0:26:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,부족한점이 많았으리라 생각돼지만 재미있게 봐주세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.32,0:26:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,&nbsp